imdb.plot outline: In a round table format, Uncover brings together top young professionals in different fields including Music, Fashion, Art, Entertainment, Science, Sports, and Business, to discuss different life topics concerning youth in today's society. These successful entrepreneurs have mastered the art of living, one-way or another and will share their insights on professional yet personal discussion topics, to help youth make better life decisions at the early stages.
